resoFacts.subdivisionName: VILLAGE ON THE LAKES AT THE ARIZONA BILTMORE ESTAT

data.description:
PRESTIGIOUS GATED NEIGHBORHOOD - WATERFRONT RESORT LIVING AT THE BILTMORE ESTATES. Prime cul-de-sac lot in Gated Community of Village on the Lakes.  Beautiful and spacious Villa overlooks both the Lake and the Arizona Biltmore Links golf course. Open split floorplan with 16' ceilings, soaring windows & dramatic curved staircase. View of city lights from master suite balcony. Beautiful views from sundeck off secondary bedrooms upstairs. Guest suite/office/gym on ground level w/ patio access. South facing back patio with pavers and charming lakeside garden. Great kitchen with island, custom Cabinetry, 6-top Gas Range, Double Ovens, microwave and Sub-zero. Two car garage with storage area and direct access into home.  Minutes to Golf, shopping, and 15-min to Sky Harbor Airport. THE BILTMORE
The Biltmore community is a master-planned development located right in the heart of Phoenix, Arizona and one of the most affluent districts in the city - Made up of several unique subdivisions.  
Area Amenities
The Biltmore area gets its name from the Arizona Biltmore Resort, a part of the exclusive Waldorf-Astoria Collection. The resort was designed by a student of Frank Lloyd Wright and bears his architectural influence. 
The Biltmore also offers two 18-hole golf courses at The Arizona Biltmore Golf Club.  Its two challenging championship courses - The Links and The Estates - are living proof that the golf in Phoenix/Scottsdale area does not necessarily require that long and laborious drive to the outskirts of town.  The Biltmore area also features great shopping and restaurants at The Biltmore Fashion Park and The Esplanade. 
Biltmore Fashion Park
The original luxury-shopping destination in Phoenix is a newly polished classic. Lush lawns and shaded, flower-filled walkways lead to a wonderful shopping destination   think Saks, Ralph Lauren, Williams-Sonoma and more. A delicious collection of restaurants, including True Food Kitchen and The Capital Grille, let you order up levels of flavorful virtue. Relaxing and inviting, it's all tucked into a historic neighborhood of luxury homes, famous resorts, and glittering high-rises.
The Esplanade - (conveniently connected to Biltmore Fashion Park via a direct walkway) 
Theatre at AMC Dine-in & Cocktails at Esplanade 14
"These theatres, equipped with full kitchens, offer experiences ranging from full-service dining to express-pick up. You can enjoy a wide range of innovative menu items, drinks, and desserts all from the comfort of your seat while taking in the latest film."
